      <title>汇丰银行因操纵欧元银行间拆借利率 3200 万欧元罚款在欧盟法庭败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/hsbc-loses-eu-court-clash-over-32-million-euribor-rigging-fine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司因非法操纵欧元银行间拆借利率基准而被欧盟处以近 3,200 万欧元的反垄断罚款，但最终败诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/hsbc-loses-eu-court-clash-over-32-million-euribor-rigging-fine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:45:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Norsk Hydro 的绿色铝转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/norsk-hydro-s-green-aluminum-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场环境严峻，挪威海德鲁公司 (Norsk Hydro ASA) 将停止为其电池和绿色氢能业务提供资金，并逐步淘汰这些业务。首席执行官 Eivind Kallevik 向彭博社的 Tom Mackenzie 讲述了这对公司的可再生能源投资以及未来增长计划意味着什么。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/norsk-hydro-s-green-aluminum-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长施纳贝尔认为进一步降息的空间有限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ecb-rate-cuts-schnabel-sees-only-limited-room-for-further-reductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，欧洲央行需要警惕过度降息，因为借贷成本已经接近不再抑制经济的水平，降息可能会适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ecb-rate-cuts-schnabel-sees-only-limited-room-for-further-reductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车出售新疆生产基地 退出争议地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/volkswagen-sells-xinjiang-sites-to-leave-controversial-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迫于投资者对中国西部地区可能存在侵犯人权行为的担忧，大众汽车集团 (Volkswagen AG) 将终止其在新疆的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/volkswagen-sells-xinjiang-sites-to-leave-controversial-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海德鲁停止绿色氢能和电池项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/norsk-hydro-pulls-plug-on-green-hydrogen-and-battery-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威海德鲁公司 (Norsk Hydro ASA) 将关闭其电池材料和绿色氢业务，这进一步表明努力实现欧洲绿色能源目标的公司面临商业压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/norsk-hydro-pulls-plug-on-green-hydrogen-and-battery-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 06:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
