    <item>
      <title>欧洲将迎来乌克兰战争以来最冷冬季，带来能源风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/europe-set-for-coldest-winter-since-ukraine-war-posing-energy-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲将迎来自俄罗斯入侵乌克兰以来最寒冷的冬季，由于欧洲大陆以比平常更快的速度消耗其天然气储备，本已高企的能源成本将进一步上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/europe-set-for-coldest-winter-since-ukraine-war-posing-energy-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
